product.title: Doodle Escape
product.shortDescription: Race through sketches to the finish line as quickly as possible!
product.longDescription: Doodle Escape is a doodle-style platform game. Race to the finish line as quickly as possible! You play as "Speed", a doodle-styled character who is fast, agile, clever, determined, and simply always on-the-run. Make your way through the twist-and-turns and the ups-and-downs of a collection of doodle sketches. But lookout! Enemies lurk who are ready to stop you! Use your doodle-wit and doodle-determination to beat these guys and make it to the finish-line in record time!
product.objectiveDescription: Doodle your way through 16 fast-paced levels while racing against the clockDodge and fight against 7 different types of cute doodle-styled enemies, like the no-questions-asked "question mark"; the fearless and to-the-point "exclamation point"; and other sword-bearing punctuation marks Use more than 10 different doodle tools to help you make your way to the finish line, such as doodle-fast racing shoes; doodle-styled rocket boosters; and other doodle-useful tools

handset.model: I8200 Galaxy S III mini VE
